🌱 RISING ACTION 1 – The First Connection

(Classroom after school.)

(Ami is surrounded by Mika and Yuna. Haru sits by the window with Ken and Sora.)

Ken:
Bro, you’ve been staring at clouds again.

Sora:
Future weather reporter?

Haru:
I just… like drawing them.

(Ami drops her notebook. Papers scatter.)

Haru:
Ah—! You dropped these!

(He hands them to her.)

Ami:
Thank you… Haru.

(He freezes.)

Haru:
Y-you know my name?

Ami:
You sit by the window. You’re always drawing.
I think it’s… kind of nice.

(Mika whispers to Yuna.)

Mika:
Why is she talking to him?

(Haru watches Ami walk away, confused but smiling.)

⸻

🌧 RISING ACTION 2 – Distance and Doubt

(Hallway. It starts raining outside.)

Sora:
Forgot your umbrella again?

Haru:
Yeah…

(Ami runs up with her umbrella.)

Ami:
Haru!

Haru:
Ami?!

Ami:
You forgot yesterday too.

(Before he can reply, Riku appears.)

Riku:
Ami. Why are you standing with him?

Ami:
He’s just a classmate.

Riku (smirking):
You don’t need to worry about guys like that.

(Haru looks down.)

Ken (quietly):
That dude’s messed up…

Riku:
Come on, Ami. Don’t waste time.

(Ami hesitates… then leaves with Riku, glancing back at Haru.)

⸻

🌤 RISING ACTION 3 – The Truth on the Rooftop

(Next day. Rooftop.)

(Ken and Sora leave Haru alone.)

Ken:
Rooftop scenes mean drama. We’re out.

(Ami appears.)

Ami:
Can I sit here?

Haru:
…Sure.

Ami:
Everyone thinks I’m lucky.
Good grades, lots of friends, a boyfriend…

Haru:
Aren’t you?

Ami:
Not really.
Riku only likes the “perfect Ami.”
Not the one who gets tired… or scared.

(She looks at his sketchbook.)

Ami:
When you draw the sky, you look free.

Haru:
It doesn’t care who’s popular.

(They share a quiet moment.)

⸻

⚡ CLIMAX – The Confrontation

(Hallway after school. Riku sees Ami laughing with Haru.)

Riku:
So this is why you’ve been avoiding me?

(Students gather.)

Ami:
Riku, stop.

Riku:
You’re choosing him over me?

Haru:
I’m not trying to steal her.

Riku:
Stay out of this, loser.

(Ami steps forward.)

Ami:
No.
I’m tired of pretending I’m happy with you.

Riku:
You’ll regret throwing this away.

Ami:
Maybe.
But I’ll regret staying more.

(Silence. Riku scoffs and walks off.)

⸻

🍃 FALLING ACTION 1 – After the Storm

(Courtyard.)

Yuna:
Ami… are you okay?

Ami:
I think… I finally am.

Mika:
You actually smiled today.

(Across the yard.)

Ken:
Dude… you survived the final boss.

Sora:
Bro unlocked the good ending route.

Haru:
I just… told the truth.

⸻

🌈 FALLING ACTION 2 – New Normal

(Ami and Haru walk home. Both friend groups follow at a distance.)

Ami:
I was scared to be alone.

Haru:
I was scared to be seen.

Ami:
Maybe we can be scared… together.

(He nods.)

⸻

🌸 RESOLUTION – Happy Ending

(Under one umbrella.)

Haru:
Why did you notice me?

Ami:
Because you looked at the world… not at me.
And somehow, that made me feel real.

(They smile shyly.)

Narrator:
When the girl everyone watched chose the boy no one saw,
they both learned what it meant to be truly seen.

END
